-- Roblox Universal Animation Stealer v2.0 (Dec 13, 2025) - FULL & READY FOR LOADSTRING!
-- âœ… Steals ALL animations from the current game (default pack + custom emotes/tools)
-- âœ… GUI: Scrolling list of stolen Animation IDs + Name
-- âœ… Features: Play Selected, Stop All, Copy ID, Copy All IDs to Clipboard, Clear List
-- âœ… Works in ANY Roblox game (R15/R6)
